# Email — contact form delivery via Resend (https://resend.com)
# 1. Sign up at resend.com using ceckomichal@gmail.com
# 2. Create an API key, paste it here as the value
# 3. (Optional, after verifying cecko.dev domain at Resend) set CONTACT_FROM
#    to e.g. "Michal Čečko <noreply@cecko.dev>". Until verification, leave
#    unset and the API will fall back to onboarding@resend.dev — emails will
#    still land in your inbox at ceckomichal@gmail.com.
RESEND_API_KEY=
# CONTACT_FROM=Michal Čečko <noreply@cecko.dev>
# CONTACT_TO=ceckomichal@gmail.com
